minescence and atomic-resolution images confirm the high\ncrystallinity of the monolayers and the seamless lateral connectivity between\nthe different TMD domains. These findings could be extended to other families\nof 2D materials, and creates the foundation towards the development of complex\nand atomically thin in-plane super-lattices, devices and integrated circuits.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Jun 2017 17:11:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-08"}
